welcome_description:
E hoʻopau i kēia kumu aʻo pōkole no kahi bonus aʻoaʻo hoʻokipa kūikawā.

Hoʻokahi minuke wale nō!
free_spins_description:
I kēlā me kēia lā a i ʻole pule āu e komo ai, e hāʻawi ʻia kāu moʻokāki i kēlā me kēia lā 'Free Spins' a me nā 'Mystery Boxes' i kēlā me kēia pule.

ʻO ka helu i loaʻa iā ʻoe ma muli o kāu pae moʻokāki.
daily_streak_description:
I kēlā me kēia lā ke komo ʻoe a loaʻa ka helu liʻiliʻi o nā kālā, hiki iā ʻoe ke koi i kāu streak i kēlā me kēia lā.

ʻOi aku ka nui o nā lā āu e koi ai i kāu streak, ʻoi aku ka nui o ka uku!

Loaʻa i nā pae moʻokāki kiʻekiʻe nā uku nui aʻe.
ptc_ads_description:
E nānā i nā hoʻolaha PTC no nā hoʻolaha wikiwiki a pōkole e hoʻonui i kāu huina kālā i kēlā me kēia lā.

E wehe ʻia ka hoʻolaha ma kahi ʻaoʻao hou, no laila e wehe ʻia a hiki i ka pau ʻana o ka manawa!
missions_description:
E ʻike ʻoe i nā haneli o nā mikiona a me nā ʻimi e hoʻopau ma ka ʻāpana 'Missions' o ka pūnaewele.

ʻO ka hoʻopau ʻana i nā misionari a me nā ʻimi he ala maikaʻi loa ia e loaʻa ai nā kālā bonus.

E nānā i ka ʻaoʻao Earn → 'Bonus Missions' no nā kikoʻī.
offers_description:
ʻO ka hoʻopiha ʻana i nā makana ʻo ia kekahi o nā ala maikaʻi loa e loaʻa ai nā kālā ma GigaFaucet.

Hiki ke loaʻa nā makana ma ka ʻāpana 'Earn' o ka pūnaewele.

Nui nā ʻano hāʻawi like ʻole i loaʻa. E nānā pono iā lākou no nā mea i hana maikaʻi loa iā ʻoe.
xp_description:
I kēlā me kēia manawa āu e hoʻopau ai i kahi hāʻawi, e pāʻani i ka multiplier, a i ʻole e nānā i kahi wikiō, a me nā mea ʻē aʻe, e loaʻa iā ʻoe ka XP (Experience Points).

ʻO ka loaʻa ʻana o XP e hoʻonui i kāu moʻokāki, e wehe ana i nā hiʻohiʻona hou aʻe a me nā uku nui aʻe.

Hiki iā ʻoe ke ʻike i kāu pae moʻokāki ma kāu ʻaoʻao Profile a i ʻole Bonuses.
withdraw_description:
Hiki iā ʻoe ke hoʻihoʻi i kāu mau kālā ke loaʻa ʻoe i ka liʻiliʻi o 30,000 mau kālā.

No ka haʻalele ʻana, e hele i ka moʻokāki → 'Cash Out' a koho i kāu ala hoʻihoʻi makemake.

E hahai i nā ʻōlelo aʻoaʻo e hoʻopau i kāu haʻalele ʻana.
all_set_description:
Ua mākaukau ʻoe e hoʻomaka i ka loaʻa kālā ma GigaFaucet!

E hoʻomanaʻo e nānā i kēlā me kēia lā no kāu mau milo bonus a me nā pahu pohihihi, a hoʻopau i nā makana a me nā misionari e hoʻonui i kāu loaʻa.

Pōmaikaʻi a hauʻoli!
